snippet.title: FIFA 23 | Official Gameplay Deep Dive
snippet.description:
Go inside FIFA 23 Gameplay with the EA SPORTS FIFA development team and see a new season of features including HyperMotion2 Technology: http://x.ea.com/74005

CHAPTERS:
00:00 - Intro
00:47 - HyperMotion2
01:56 - Women’s Club Football
02:40 - Technical Dribbling
03:31 - ML-Jockey
03:58 - AcceleRATE
05:04 - Signature Run Styles
05:54 - Attacking
06:06 - Power Shots
06:34 - Composed Ball Striking
07:01 - Set Pieces
08:02 - Defending
08:58 - Goalkeeping
09:45 - Physics
10:07 - Skill Moves

For even more on FIFA 23 Gameplay, check out the Pitch Notes: https://www.ea.com/games/fifa/fifa-23/news/pitch-notes-fifa-23-gameplay-deep-dive

FIFA 23 releases September 30, 2022 with HyperMotion2 Technology, women’s club football, both men’s and women’s FIFA World Cup™ tournaments, cross-play features, and more: http://x.ea.com/74006

Pre-order FIFA 23 Ultimate Edition by August 21 to get a FIFA World Cup™ FUT Hero item, as well as up to three days early access: http://x.ea.com/74007

Subscribe to see more FIFA 23 videos: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.

#FIFA23 #TheWorldsGame #HyperMotion2

Note that these clips were recorded during the development of FIFA 23, and information within it may change or become updated over time as we finalize the development of FIFA 23.
